'''1-二十二醇'''（'''Docosanol'''）是一种饱和一元脂肪醇，是化妆品传统的润肤剂，乳化剂，增稠剂。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://fleur-s-cosmetics.stalgroup.com/ |title=Fleur's Cosmetics Canada |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archive-date=2009-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501094452/http://fleur-s-cosmetics.stalgroup.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.korresusa.com/product/4820/eye-cream/skincare/category/anti-aging- |title=Korres USA |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archive-date=2009-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090804013645/http://www.korresusa.com/product/4820/eye-cream/skincare/category/anti-aging- |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.avalonorganics.com/?id=124&show=B |title=Avalon Organics |accessdate=2013-09-18 |archive-date=2013-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130820204550/http://avalonorganics.com/?id=124&show=B |dead-url=no }}</ref>近年来，[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]（FDA）批准了其作为抗病毒药物的使用，商品名为'''Abreva'''，用于治疗[[单纯疱疹病毒|单纯疱疹病毒]]引起的冷疮。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.medilexicon.com/drugs/abreva.php |title=mediLexicon: Docosanol |access-date=2013-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310114409/http://www.medilexicon.com/drugs/abreva.php |archive-date=2013-03-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
